{"tid":1457794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建議每次發夢自發組成捉鬼隊","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:50:52.000Z","uid":236676,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9c40c5082d87dd6342bd7361e2a2d08c595c1b7f","tid":1457794,"uid":236676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:16:42.000Z","msg":"6-10人為佳，多人成團 避免 落單狗身邊有人支援<br />\n<br />\n成立捉鬼隊，去查清可疑人士既身份(耳筒狗)<br />\n<br />\n成立捉鬼隊 既成員入面 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">必須帶備自己本身既工作證或學生證等</span></span>並且互相再用身份證確認身份，(相信隻狗可以整假工作證都唔會敢拎自己張身份證出黎)避免有狗混入害成隊人。<br />\n<br />\n發夢裡面最避忌互相猜疑，而呢個方法就算一個發夢都可以組到隊，請廣傳，集思廣益。"},{"pid":"5746616f6f4d57780cfcb1c28f73141b3b4faacf","tid":1457794,"uid":75620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:17:42.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"710372dfdc73866561498286cad859d31573cc23","tid":1457794,"uid":852,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:18:17.000Z","msg":"佔中糾察？"},{"pid":"60dd1b269b1b55efbc372464450b8c446537ad6e","tid":1457794,"uid":236676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"710372dfdc73866561498286cad859d31573cc23","tid":1457794,"uid":852,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:18:17.000Z","msg":"佔中糾察？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:19:36.000Z","msg":"🤔佔中糾察係點"},{"pid":"4953949348e3b5305b25bd4ddbe4d7e25a22efe2","tid":1457794,"uid":198245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:19:50.000Z","msg":"大把真心膠㗎，現場散水撚同留守撚互屌你捉邊邊？"},{"pid":"eaf7319e7a4a861616bc0cd6928cb2017104cda8","tid":1457794,"uid":236676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4953949348e3b5305b25bd4ddbe4d7e25a22efe2","tid":1457794,"uid":198245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:19:50.000Z","msg":"大把真心膠㗎，現場散水撚同留守撚互屌你捉邊邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:21:03.000Z","msg":"最少未開波之前做"},{"pid":"ccacc4dead4650ea4f85e53dbef95336464dbff5","tid":1457794,"uid":23